</p>\n                                                                                 <a class="item" href="/index.php?a=go_pay&num_iid=42724258984" target="_blank">\n                            <div class="item-pic">\n                                <img src="http://img.alicdn.com/tps/i1/TB1CitNIVXXXXaqaXXXXXXXXXXX_!!0-item_pic.jpg">\n                            </div>\n                            <div class="item-info">\n                                <div class="item-title">巴拉巴拉童装女童娃娃领长袖T恤幼童宝宝休闲T2015儿童秋装新款</div>\n                                <div class="item-price">\n                                                                            <ins class="price-new">¥&nbsp;<strong>99.0</strong></ins>\n                                    \n                                </div>\n                                <div class="item-btn">去购买</div>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                                                                                 <p>背带裤也是非常适合宝宝在秋天穿的衣服，胸前绘有一只小熊的图案，给整条裤子增色不少。 </p>\n                                                                                 <a class="item" href="/index.php?a=go_pay&num_iid=43050862593" target="_blank">\n                            <div class="item-pic">\n                                <img src="http://img.alicdn.com/tps/i2/TB1y2PqHVXXXXbwXFXXXXXXXXXX_!!0-item_pic.jpg">\n                            </div>\n                            <div class="item-info">\n                                <div class="item-title">小数点童装宝宝背带裤春秋装弹力牛仔休闲男童背带裤儿童吊带长裤</div>\n                                <div class="item-price">\n                                                                            <ins class="price-new">¥&nbsp;<strong>100.0</strong></ins>\n                                    \n                                </div>\n                                <div class="item-btn">去购买</div>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                       